> pe(feTR) summary_measures

Under the common trends assumption,
the TWFE coefficient beta, equal to 0.0545, estimates a weighted sum of 196 ATT
> s. 
182 ATTs receive a positive weight, and 14 receive a negative weight.
------------------------------------------------
Treat. var: gncs        # ATTs      Σ weights  
------------------------------------------------
Positive weights        182         1.0406      
Negative weights        14          -0.0406     
------------------------------------------------
Total                   196         1.0000      
------------------------------------------------

Summary Measures:
TWFE coefficient (β_fe) =    0.0545
min σ(Δ) compatible with β_fe and Δ_TR = 0:    0.0795
min σ(Δ) compatible with treatment effect of opposite sign than β_fe in all (g,
> t) cells:    0.2730
